snippet.title: DOGS trying to KISS EVERYTHING are so FUNNY! - PREPARE to LAUGH!
snippet.description:
These kissing dogs are so funny and absolutely adorable! Just look how all these dogs and puppies kiss and lick cats, babies, kids, owners,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
